item.description: This is a leash required place for walking, but it is really pretty and a good walk. There are little trails along the water's edge, and then a large clear path that people run, bike, and take their dogs on. There are a few boat docking areas along the way, so you can see more water and take a break at a picnic table or grassy area. My dog and his k9 buddy really enjoyed this walk! This is a popular picnic and walking place.
